snippet.title: ROCHE LIMIT: The Death of CMK | PowerPoint Horror Game Playthrough [No Commentary]
snippet.description:
Feel free to like and subscribe!

ROCHE LIMIT: The Death of CMK is a horror-surrealist style PowerPoint game I made over the course of eight months. It features over 1,500 slides and 80+ unique hand drawn scenes. The game's a follow-up to my 2019 project The EdCo Incident which can be watched here:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZHpQDkEae7o

Click below to download and play ROCHE LIMIT for yourself! (With more endings coming soon!) 
PowerPoint 2016 or newer is highly recommended 
https://www.mediafire.com/file/n1gs23agwb7wl2q/ROCHE_LIMIT_%255BRelease_V2.2%255D.zip/file

Also consider checking out the game's two trailers!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=436UhccpZcM
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qZHeleeZZWg
